  • Classes in aves.dpt.intf.production used by aves.dpt.impl.production 
    Class and Description
    AvesObject
    Interface defining the type of the objects presented in Aves JOURNEYS.
    AvesObject.AvesObjectType
    Defines objects depending on the AvesManager.Phase when it will be used during a Aves JOURNEYS.
    AvesObject.ObjectDataType
    defines the AvesObject.ObjectDataType.
    DataRetriever
    Classes implementing this interface extract the source DOCUMENTS in the aves/Journeys/avesJourneys.xml file for the Factory that manages how AvesObjects are added to the list that is returned to the AvesManager.
    Factory
    Classes implementing this interface request the production of a List of AvesObjects that the AvesManager manages during a specific AvesManager.Phase.
    Factory.ProductionMode
    Defines the different modes of production that will themselves define the AvesObject.AvesObjectType requested by the Factory.
    XMLDataReader
    Objects implementing this interface retrieve DOCUMENTS with specific tags from the aves/Journeys/avesJourneys.xml file
